data.description: At last! The home of your dreams is awaiting new owners! Nestled on a premium corner lot, this 1,800 sqft property offers a low-care front yard and a 2-car garage. Desirable open floor layout showcases recessed lighting, gorgeous wood-look flooring, & bountiful natural light. You'll love the living area featuring pre-wired surround sound, a custom wall, & multi-sliders to the back patio. The impeccable kitchen has granite counters, tile backsplash, crown moulding cabinetry, a walk-in pantry, & an island with a breakfast bar. Retreat to the main suite boasting backyard access & a private bathroom w/walk-in closet & a dual sink vanity. The well-sized backyard invites you to unwind under the covered patio with artificial turf & a lovely view fence.
